{"tid":1903260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情擴散近50國 世衛調高全球風險至「非常高」","createTime":"2020-02-28T23:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T01:25:54.000Z","uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b42a91536861d5100a62f1bf8370017bfee20b","tid":1903260,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:28:27.000Z","msg":"疫情擴散近50國 世衛調高全球風險至「非常高」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/202002290444516351_45N201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F202002290444516351_45N201.jpg&h=92080545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世衛組織秘書長譚德塞今天宣布，將2019年冠狀病毒全球風險提升為「非常高」。(Getty Images)<br />\n世界衛生組織今天宣布，將2019年冠狀病毒全球風險提升為「非常高」，說明目前在中國以外有49國出現病毒感染案例，愈來愈多國家受影響現象相當令人關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=49&amp;v=85ZX3v6z1uQ&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D49%26v%3D85ZX3v6z1uQ%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT24VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=5cd7c3b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=49&amp;v=85ZX3v6z1uQ&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n影片來源：YouTube USA Today<br />\n<br />\n世衛組織秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）今天下午出席日內瓦記者會，說明2019年冠狀病毒（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情最新情況時做以上宣布 。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞表示，截至今天上午，中國向世衛組織（WHO）報告了7萬8959個病例，其中死亡2791例，雖然過去24小時中國新增329病例，是一個多月以來的最低數量。但在中國境外，目前在49個國家共有4351例病例，死亡67例。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，最近幾天愈來愈多國家出現病例，相當令人關注，世衛流行病學家監測這些發展，現在已將病毒全球風險自「高」提升至「非常高」，向全球發出更強警訊。<br />\n<br />\n但世衛強調，目前大多數病例仍可追溯到已知的接觸者或病例群，尚無證據表明病毒正在社區中廣泛傳播。<br />\n<br />\n世衛公布昨天丹麥，愛沙尼亞，立陶宛，荷蘭都出現首例，而所有這些案例都與義大利有關。另表示全球正在開發多種疫苗，其中數種治療劑正在臨床試驗中，預計幾週內可以取得初步成果。"},{"pid":"3f10349714dd9723e21d53cfccc780f75daf9fb3","tid":1903260,"uid":284699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:29:51.000Z","msg":"譚德塞成功爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fa6e90baff90adaa28057b72fbc4f44c57088a","tid":1903260,"uid":102078,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:34:21.000Z","msg":"咪多得你囉，一味叫人唔洗驚 唔好做歧視性措施，<br />\n咁你做乜撚野世衛呀 ，執撚左佢啦，改做中國衛生部啦仆街"},{"pid":"b450c1d69e3e7176ff9c5307fd0b5b1ebbf107af","tid":1903260,"uid":44462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:37:03.000Z","msg":"尚無證據表明病毒正在社區中廣泛傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燈到就黎有"},{"pid":"0ab999681ee8c4be491f4542cf76c037f5fd2c82","tid":1903260,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:39:28.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係要上斷頭台<br />\n<br />\n成個世界俾你玩死"},{"pid":"1199cd1f99aef58506567488428d60b4f6c54659","tid":1903260,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab999681ee8c4be491f4542cf76c037f5fd2c82","tid":1903260,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:39:28.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係要上斷頭台<br />\n<br />\n成個世界俾你玩死"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"應該好快俾其他國家提出落台換人<br />\n<br />\n到時主席位都冇埋 支那又唔洗養多個傻鳩 真係兩頭唔到岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5016dddd51c6491fccbd3f74d810672339c038","tid":1903260,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1199cd1f99aef58506567488428d60b4f6c54659","tid":1903260,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab999681ee8c4be491f4542cf76c037f5fd2c82","tid":1903260,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:39:28.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係要上斷頭台<br />\n<br />\n成個世界俾你玩死"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"應該好快俾其他國家提出落台換人<br />\n<br />\n到時主席位都冇埋 支那又唔洗養多個傻鳩 真係兩頭唔到岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T23:44:44.000Z","msg":"係 director general 總幹事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr